# {{ .projectName }}

Traefik reverse proxy with Docker provider auto-discovery.

## Quick Start

    docker compose up -d

## Access

* HTTP: http://localhost:{{ .httpPort }}
* HTTPS: https://localhost:{{ .httpsPort }}
* Dashboard: http://localhost:{{ .dashboardPort }}/dashboard/

## Exposing a Service

Add these labels to any container on the traefik_net network:

    labels:
      traefik.enable: "true"
      traefik.http.routers.myapp.rule: Host(`myapp.localhost`)
      traefik.http.services.myapp.loadbalancer.server.port: "3000"
